#### IX

<div style="font-size: 90%">

The *Wu I;* narrative. A request to the king's envoy for the
acknowledgment of Duke Wu as marquis of Chin.

</div>

<div style="margin-left: 20%; margin-right: 20%; font-size: 110%;">

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_1">1</span></span>State robes can he
be said to want?  
  His robes the seven high symbols show.  
But let him have them by your grant:—  
  That peace and fortune will bestow.

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2">2</span></span>State robes can he
be said to want?  
  The symbols six his robes display.  
But let him have them by your grant,  
  And that will lasting peace convey.

</div>

